msgid "Graph analysis"
msgstr "Analyse de graphe"

#: ../../docs/pyqgis_developer_cookbook/network_analysis.rst:202
msgid ""
"The shortest path tree is a directed weighted graph (or more precisely a "
"tree) with the following properties:"
msgstr ""
"L'arbre du chemin le plus court est un graphique pondéré dirigé (ou plus "
"précisément un arbre) ayant les propriétés suivantes :"

#: ../../docs/pyqgis_developer_cookbook/network_analysis.rst:205
msgid "only one vertex has no incoming edges — the root of the tree"
msgstr "Seul un arc n'a pas d'arcs entrants: la racine de l'arbre."

#: ../../docs/pyqgis_developer_cookbook/network_analysis.rst:207
msgid ""
"if vertex B is reachable from vertex A, then the path from A to B is the "
"single available path and it is optimal (shortest) on this graph"
msgstr ""
"Si un arc B est atteignable depuis l'arc A alors le chemin de A vers B est "
"le seul chemin disponible et il est le chemin optimal (le plus court) sur ce"
" graphe."

#: ../../docs/pyqgis_developer_cookbook/network_analysis.rst:210
msgid ""
"To get the shortest path tree use the methods :meth:`shortestTree() "
"<qgis.analysis.QgsGraphAnalyzer.shortestTree>` and :meth:`dijkstra() "
"<qgis.analysis.QgsGraphAnalyzer.dijkstra>` of the :class:`QgsGraphAnalyzer "
"<qgis.analysis.QgsGraphAnalyzer>` class. It is recommended to use the "
":meth:`dijkstra() <qgis.analysis.QgsGraphAnalyzer.dijkstra>` method because "
"it works faster and uses memory more efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Pour obtenir l'arbre du chemin le plus court, utilisez les méthodes "
":meth:`shortestTree() <qgis.analysis.QgsGraphAnalyzer.shortestTree>` et "
":meth:`dijkstra() <qgis.analysis.QgsGraphAnalyzer.dijkstra>` de la classe "
":class:`QgsGraphAnalyzer <qgis.analysis.QgsGraphAnalyzer>`. Il est "
"recommandé d'utiliser la méthode :meth:`dijkstra() "
"<qgis.analysis.QgsGraphAnalyzer.dijkstra>` car elle fonctionne plus "
"rapidement et utilise la mémoire de manière plus efficace."

